title: Looking for low elo players who want to climb
body:
Not your classic, "I'm bronze but should be challenger" post. I get disheartened by poor team mates and would much prefer to duo with someone who can help me carry. Went from b3 to b5 in a day so im on perma-tilt. Add me! 
I main JG (Hec/Lee Sin/Olaf/Master Yi)
I can also play any other role more than comfortably
IGN - Reggiedevil
